Add stadium upper tier: stairs → viewing deck → Trophy Room + VIP Lounge

Each plot now has a second level on the east side: an auto-climbable staircase up
to a viewing deck with gold railings. On the deck: an enclosed Trophy Room (three
podiums with golden cups + a sign) and an open VIP Lounge (plush neon floor, sign,
benches). Tagged "UpperTier".

